2},"title":"Hadith on Emancipation: Freeing slaves protects one from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Whoever emancipates a believing slave, Allah will free every organ of his from Hellfire in equal measure.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1509 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37972,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/19\/tawhid-haram-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":15564,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Declaring Allah\u2019s oneness protects from Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever testified that there is no God but Allah and Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah, then Allah will forbid him from the Hellfire.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 29 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abu